{"tid":2356080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同事: 今年業績唔好可能要落多D廣告。冷嘲熱諷撚: 岩呀落完廣告皇帝都有得你做，我支持落廣告架，又唔岩聽?","createTime":"2021-01-06T14:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T15:12:37.000Z","uid":31215,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c17637da074ec87459b78279f5397499176e8e","tid":2356080,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"想問下冷嘲熱諷撚平時係咪咁同人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地屌佢咁講野嬲屌<br />\n冷嘲熱諷就會話我都係講事實，佢唔做柒野講柒野，咪冇人冷嘲熱諷到囉，自己唔檢討仲話人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n似乎佢地唔識點樣將一個message 好好地講出黎<br />\n要用呢種講法消磨人意志<br />\n同一個內容，正常講同冷嘲熱諷已經差好遠啦<br />\n<br />\n冷嘲熱諷講黎講去都話人屈毛，所以自己就要冷嘲熱瘋<br />\n或者講完自己觀點，人地唔認同，就要冷嘲熱諷人<br />\n<br />\n屌啦<br />\n你唔妥人屈毛，正正經經講唔得嘅<br />\n人地唔認同自己觀點，可以講多幾次，可以收皮，我開左咁多個post 你都唔認同我啦<br />\n唔使下下放負咩都走去冷嘲熱諷人嘅<br />\n譬如有人仍然覺得要街頭抗爭/35+/眾籌/食黃店，你講完唔應該去嘅觀點，佢唔認同，都係要去，咁你一係算，一係再同佢講，你單打佢做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨post 附上冷嘲熱諷撚四大詭辯方法，大家見到唔好被fake<br />\n<br />\n1. 煞有介事咁反問<br />\n例如你打完一堆論點<br />\n就問你一句<br />\n你知咩叫民主架可?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有野就清清楚楚講，唔好扮哂意味深遠<br />\n<br />\n2. 無限滑坡<br />\n例子: 講下都唔俾，咁手足強姦都唔俾講，勿分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用極端化嘅強姦類比抗爭方式嘅討論<br />\n任何正常野一極端化一定出問題，然後就因為呢個偽問題否定返你個正常野<br />\n<br />\n3. 你都有錯你唔講?<br />\n例子: 我話冷嘲熱諷有問題，D人就話，咁你點睇邊個邊個屈毛? 唔見你講下?<br />\n你咁想講其他野咪自己開post講，A有冇錯唔影響我話B錯<br />\n<br />\n4. 發悔氣<br />\n呢個最討厭<br />\n例子: 傾35+ 有冇用<br />\n講完一大論說服唔到人，就話得得得，我最支持一國兩制，體制內抗爭，邊個再反就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用道理說服唔到人就flip去對面立場嘅極端繼續單打<br />\n呢個有圖俾大家參考下<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jo8zZc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jo8zZc.png&h=274564cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgYMmEc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgYMmEc.png&h=2edef1f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oxt1axy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxt1axy.png&h=d710fa47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae1e4fcafb2e60acfdf06927e23ba91ac8bd8887","tid":2356080,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5de7976f76b1443302a6f558060e1054e292c61","tid":2356080,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c05c70e5e12c663e507309d5ca48150a87cecb0","tid":2356080,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"見到呢d人真係字都廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覆都唔撚覆就最好"},{"pid":"9bf19d1187760314168c0892a6fd13ce004f7f57","tid":2356080,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c05c70e5e12c663e507309d5ca48150a87cecb0","tid":2356080,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:28:20.000Z","msg":"見到呢d人真係字都廢事打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覆都唔撚覆就最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:34:48.000Z","msg":"一多起上黎好消磨人意志<br />\n<br />\n佢地仲會話返你廢<br />\n講兩講就受影響<br />\n<br />\n冷嘲熱諷係會影響人鬥志不容否認"},{"pid":"fe5312eb06c23b177eaf5c142d02e7b18cefebf9","tid":2356